This is an unbeatable game of Tic Tac Toe played via a console or a gui.

To play the console version, simply run: ./play_console

You will be presented with a menu.
Enter 0 to play against a friend.
Enter 1 to play against the computer.
Enter 2 to watch the computer play against itself.

To play the GUI version, you must be running JRuby with the Limelight
gem installed.  This game was tested with JRuby 1.6.7 and Limelight 0.5.5.
If these requirements are met, simply run: ./play_gui

Currently, you can only play against the computer with the GUI version.
